Name: Boost

Object: /d/Sparkle/guilds/arcane/spells/boost.c

Cost: 

Skills: 

Description: Tier 1 spell
		    Targets: 1, unspecified target defaults to caster
		 This is a stat increaser. Increases either strength,
		 constitution or dexterity at random, caster can not
		 choose which. The spell is more effective on the
		 caster than on a third party target. At Master level,
		 the spell will minimally increase all three physicals.

Requirements:
    SS_ELEMENT_WATER
    SS_FORM_CONJURATION
    Wine
